\/23\/shahadah-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":25831,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Shahada: Testimony of faith leads to Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 23, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cKnow that whoever testifies 'there is no God but Allah' will enter Paradise.\u201d Source: al-Sunan al-Kubra\u0301 lil-Nasa\u0304\u2019i\u0304 10906 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Busiri \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0650\u0643\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39836,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/21\/shahadah-hijab-nar\/","url_meta":{"origin":25831,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Shahadah: Testimony of faith protects from Hellfire","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 21, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu \u2018Amrah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI testify there is no God but Allah and I am the Messenger of Allah. I testify before Allah that no believing servant meets Him with these two statements but he will be shielded from the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39838,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/21\/shahadah-necessitates-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":25831,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Shahadah: Testimony of faith necessitates Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 21, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Suhayl ibn Bayda\u2019 reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, whoever testifies there is no God but Allah, then Allah will forbid him from entering Hellfire and require him to enter Paradise.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 199 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11074,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/06\/four-articles-of-faith\/","url_meta":{"origin":25831,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Iman: No true faith until he believes in four things","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali ibn Abi Talib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo one has faith until he believes in four things: He testifies there is no God but Allah, and I am the Messenger of Allah sent with the truth, he believes in the resurrection\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"h